                                                                                   DestinationCard))
                                                                "Untitled")
                                                         (NC.FetchNewCardFlg DestinationCard))
                                                    then NIL
                                                  else OldTitle)
                                                T Window))
                          then (NC.AssignTitle DestinationCard NIL NewTitle)
                               'CHANGED))))))))))(DEFINEQ(NC.DeleteBadPointer
